{"app_type": "privileged", "author": "Codexa", "categories": ["productivity", "utilities"], "content_ratings": {"ratings": null, "interactive_elements": null, "descriptors": null}, "created": "2013-05-07T14:25:31", "current_version": "0.3", "default_locale": "en-US", "device_types": ["firefoxos"], "description": {"el": "\u0388\u03bd\u03b1 \u03ba\u03b5\u03af\u03bc\u03b5\u03bd\u03bf-editor \u03b3\u03b9\u03b1 \u03c4\u03bf\u03bd Firefox OS", "fr": "Un \u00e9diteur de texte pour Firefox OS", "en-US": "A word processor for Firefox OS that gives users professional productivity power in their pockets.  Firetext also can be used to take notes and edit plain-text files.\n\n<b>Note:</b> some users have been reporting issues with Firetext running on Firefox OS 1.0.  Firetext is not compatible with that version of Firefox OS due to some changes in APIs.  Sorry!\n\nFiretext is an open-source project, driven by an awesome community, and we would love to see you involved!  Please check out our GitHub at <a href=\"http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/c001182b6f583b04509fefa75f0207aa7015916fcf7c52419e3e40435067ed0d/https%3A//github.com/Codexa/Firetext\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/Codexa/Firetext</a>.\n\n<b>Note:</b> Please report issues, give feedback and make feature requests by emailing us at support@codexa.org. Thank you!\n\n<i>This app requires an SD card, and permission to access it.  Also, the USB Mass Storage preference <b>must be turned off</b>, or there will be an error.</i>\n\n<b>Features:</b>\n<ul>  <li>Formats\n    <ul>      <li>.html</li>      <li>.txt</li>    </ul>  </li>  <li>File I/O\n    <ul>      <li>deviceStorage API</li>    </ul>  </li>  <li>Formatting\n    <ul>      <li>align</li>      <li>bold</li>      <li>italic</li>      <li>Format removal</li>      <li>strikethrough</li>      <li>underline</li>    </ul>  </li>  <li>Elements\n    <ul>      <li>horizontal rules</li>      <li>images</li>      <li>links</li>      <li>ordered list</li>      <li>tables</li>      <li>unordered list</li>    </ul>  </li>  <li>Zen Mode</li>  <li>Night Mode</li>  <li>Raw mode for HTML documents\n    <ul>      <li>Syntax highlighting</li>    </ul>  </li>  <li>Cloud services\n    <ul>      <li>Dropbox</li>    </ul>  </li>  <li>Autoload</li>  <li>Autosave</li></ul>\n<b>Future Features:</b>\n<ul>  <li>Sharing via Email, Skydrive, and Google Drive.</li>  <li>Support for RTF, ODT, and DOCX documents.</li>  <li>Speed improvements.  (<b>v0.3.1</b>)</li>  <li>Support for multiple languages.</li>  <li>Desktop app.</li>  <li>Collaborative editing with comments and revisions.</li>  <li>Integrated web search for researching.</li></ul>", "ru": "\u0422\u0435\u043a\u0441\u0442\u043e\u0432\u044b\u0439 \u0440\u0435\u0434\u0430\u043a\u0442\u043e\u0440 \u0434\u043b\u044f Firefox OS", "zh-TW": "\u6587\u672c\u7f16\u8f91\u5668\uff0c\u706b\u72d0OS", "de": "Ein Text-Editor f\u00fcr Firefox OS", "tr": "Firefox OS i\u00e7in bir metin edit\u00f6r\u00fc", "it": "Un editor di testo per Firefox OS", "ar": "\u0645\u062d\u0631\u0631 \u0646\u0635\u0648\u0635 \u0644\u0641\u0627\u064a\u0631\u0641\u0648\u0643\u0633 OS", "pt-BR": "Um editor de texto para Firefox OS", "es": "Un editor de texto para Firefox OS"}, "homepage": {"en-US": "http://firetext.codexa.org"}, "icons": {"16": "https://marketplace.cdn.mozilla.net/img/uploads/addon_icons/437/437142-32.png?modified=1386947565", "48": "https://marketplace.cdn.mozilla.net/img/uploads/addon_icons/437/437142-48.png?modified=1386947565", "128": "https://marketplace.cdn.mozilla.net/img/uploads/addon_icons/437/437142-128.png?modified=1386947565", "64": "https://marketplace.cdn.mozilla.net/img/uploads/addon_icons/437/437142-64.png?modified=1386947565"}, "id": 437142, "is_packaged": true, "manifest_url": "https://marketplace.firefox.com/app/dbda1496-05f5-462b-8c4d-fc1b2aaa20d0/manifest.webapp", "name": {"el": "Firetext", "fr": "Firetext", "en-US": "Firetext", "ru": "Firetext", "zh-TW": "Firetext", "de": "Firetext", "tr": "Firetext", "it": 